1 (6) Cooperate with the Kentucky Ohio River Regional Recreation Authority
2 established in KRS 148.034 for the purpose of establishing, maintaining, and
3 promoting recreational trails to increase economic development, tourism, and
4 outdoor recreation for Kentucky's residents and visitors, not only along the Ohio
5 River but throughout the Commonwealth.
